  /*
  
  ### NamingConventions ###

  TokeTypes: 
    "TokenTypes-color": "BackgroundColor; BorderColor; IconColor; TextColor ",
    "TokenTypes-dimensions": "Size, IconSize, BorderWidth, BorderRadius, PaddingTop, Width, Height...",
    "TokenTypes-borders": "Border"
    "TokenTypes-typos": "Typography"

  Element:
    an Element must be named. If the the Element is the outer container of the component I use "Container" 

  Sentiments:
     "Default; Mute; Inverted; Neutral; Warning; Error"

  ToggleStates:
    "Active": "Replaces Selected everywhere",
    "Inactive": "Replaces Unselected everywhere"

  LayoutVariant:
    "Vertical, Horizontal"
    (Use if the component comes in different layouts as seen in StepperCombo)

  "SizeVariants": 
    "XS, SM, MD, LG, XL"

  "UserInteractions": 
    "Rest, Hover, Pressed..."

*/

  /* 


###  CMP tokens - dimensions und colors zusammengefasst, müssen aber in einzelne files später"

  Bug: "Radio und Checkbox sind eigentlich gleich. Aber das naming stimmt nicht überein (ContentRow vs Container)" - Fixed!,
  Bug: Radio.ContentRow.Padding kann weg? oder muss auch auf checkbox angelegt werden
  Improvement: Radio did only have a single size control. I'd like to add Conrols for all size variants. Tokens are now added.
  "Outdated 1": "Dimensions/CMP:Select.IconPaddingRight tokens sind outdated? Ich glaube Input.ItemSpacing und Input.Padding sollte reichen",

  Checkbox.Control.Border tokens are much more granular now. Added size, added Selected-state
  Checkbox.Container.Size is much simpler now. It will not respect any states anymore, as this is quite unlikely a requirement
  Checkbox.Icon.Size is much simpler now. It will not respect the toggle states anymore, as this is quite unlikely a requirement. (Interaction states are still respected)


*/

